OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777039866
OL,3,CLiverpool fans express 'deep concern'
OL,4,Cin letter to owner
OL,6,FLiverpool FC fans have written to
OL,7,Fprincipal owner John Henry expressing
OL,8,Ftheir concerns after the introduction
OL,9,Fof ticket price rises for the next
OL,10,Fthree years.
OL,12,FLiverpool Supporters Board wrote the
OL,13,Fopen letter after their request for a
OL,14,Ffreeze on the inflation-linked
OL,15,Fincreases was rejected.
OL,17,FIn the letter, they said they felt
OL,18,F"deep concern for the future direction
OL,19,Fof the club".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
