PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777039866
OL,3,CLiverpool fans express 'deep concern'
OL,4,Cin letter to owner
OL,6,FFans held a protest at their last home
OL,7,Fmatch against Fulham on 11 April.
OL,8,FFurther action is planned for their
OL,9,Fvisit to Crystal Palace, where they
OL,10,Fintend on raising thousands of yellow
OL,11,Fcards during the 13th minute.
OL,13,FSimilar tactics in 2016, with walkouts
OL,14,Fstaged in opposition against a #70
OL,15,Fmatch ticket, resulted in owners
OL,16,FFenway Sports Group performing a U-
OL,17,Fturn.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777039866
OL,3,CLiverpool fans express 'deep concern'
OL,4,Cin letter to owner
OL,6,FThe letter said: "We don't believe you
OL,7,Fare listening to Liverpool supporters
OL,8,Fright now regarding your decision to
OL,9,Fmake the club the first to commit to a
OL,10,Fpolicy of locking in three years of
OL,11,Fgeneral admission price rises
OL,13,F"That is deeply concerning for the
OL,14,Ffuture direction of this club and
OL,15,FEnglish football in general.
OL,16,FSupporters have been clear in their
OL,17,Fopposition to the introduction of
OL,18,Fmulti-year price rises.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777039866
OL,3,CLiverpool fans express 'deep concern'
OL,4,Cin letter to owner
OL,6,F"Not simply because of the increase
OL,7,Fitself, but because of what it
OL,8,Frepresents: the removal of meaningful
OL,9,Fannual dialogue, and a shift towards a
OL,10,Fmodel where prices are set for years
OL,11,Fin advance, regardless of supporter
OL,12,Fsentiment, and any financial realities
OL,13,Fthey or the club may face.
OL,15,F"Decisions like this, particularly
OL,16,Fwhen set over multiple years, do not
OL,17,Fjust affect affordability in the
OL,18,Fpresent, they shape who is able to
OL,19,Fattend matches in the future and in
OL,20,Fdoing so, they shape what the club
OL,21,Fbecomes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777039866
OL,3,CLiverpool fans express 'deep concern'
OL,4,Cin letter to owner
OL,6,F"Supporter concern is that future
OL,7,Fgenerations ` their children,
OL,8,Fgrandchildren and beyond ` will not be
OL,9,Fable to do what they have done before."
OL,11,FIt is understood that Liverpool have
OL,12,Freached out to the Supporters Board
OL,13,Fand other groups like Spirit of
OL,14,FShankly, expressing their desire to
OL,15,Fmaintain lines of communication.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777039866
OL,3,CLiverpool fans express 'deep concern'
OL,4,Cin letter to owner
OL,6,FThe club says the reason for price
OL,7,Fincreases is that matchday operating
OL,8,Fcosts have risen 85 per cent since
OL,9,F2016-17, insisting adult season
OL,10,Ftickets would increase by no more than
OL,11,F#3.50 per game across three years with
OL,12,Fgeneral admission tickets increasing
OL,13,Fbetween #3 and #4.50 over the same
OL,14,Fperiod.
OL,16,FThey also pointed out that current
OL,17,Fmatch ticket prices on the Kop are the
OL,18,Fsame as they were when owners Fenway
OL,19,FSports Group took over more than 15
OL,20,Fyears ago against a backdrop of 45%
OL,21,Fcumulative inflation during that time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
